            </svg>
            <span class="text-sm font-bold text-purple-700">4.9/5 Stars from 2,847 Reviews</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-foreground mb-4">Loved By Customers</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground">Join thousands of satisfied customers who have experienced the ONE difference.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
